com.softwareag.security.jaas.login

Class SagCredentials

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.softwareag.security.jaas.login.SagCredentials
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SagCredentials
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Generic credentials queried by SagCallbackHandler, and evaluated by the LoginModules. All LoginModules derived from SagAbstractLoginModule get these SagCredentials.
    See Also:
